name: Glitch Runner
description:
Phantom Series - No.5:

A voxel based humanoid entity gets bit shifted by invisible forces. This marks the beginning of the shift into synthwave territory for the aesthetic undertone of the film.

video | 1080 x 1080 | 30fps
